01:42.720 --> 01:43.870
dan cuba membunuh saya.

01:44.280 --> 01:45.870
Tidak bolehkah saya melawan?

01:47.870 --> 01:49.110
Kata Putera Minglang

01:49.560 --> 01:52.640
putera tebusan

01:53.110 --> 01:55.670
Tantai Minglang mahu saya bunuh dia?

01:58.390 --> 01:59.030
Yingxin.

01:59.510 --> 02:00.230
Adakah awak ingat

